    <main>
      <h2>He Didn’t See Me</h2>
      
      <div class="content">
	<p>
	  He didn’t see me, did he?<br>
A dingy old Mazda,<br>
Pulled out of nowhere<br>
	  In front of me, 80 k’s
	</p>

	<p>
An hour, eyes missing<br>
From the back of his head<br>
No time to stop or look<br>
Away, screech, crunch
	</p>

	<p>
The nose of my car<br>
Sliding into his door<br>
Like the forlorn lance<br>
Of Longinus,
	</p>

	<p>
Draw forward,<br> 
Explosive punch<br>
Of the airbag with the<br> 
Noise of clouds turning grey
	</p>

	<p>
Me the Pontius Pilate,<br>
Spited nose, ambos<br>
Checking my airway,<br>
The chassis popped in
	</p>

	<p>
Like a used<br>
Blister pack<br>
Was a bad omen but<br>
I knew for sure when they
	</p>

	<p>
Put the blanket over his head.
	  </p>
      </div>
      
